e."}},"step_CbgTRp":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Courtney T.","filter_tag":"eczema","line_1_text":"Will Definitely Buy Again","line_2_text":"A little goes a long way. It helped clear my son’s eczema. I also use it on my face as a daily moisturizer. It’s not greasy and absorbs well into my skin without leaving my face shiny. Overall great product."}},"step_VJrx89":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Frank A.","filter_tag":"dry","line_1_text":"You Have To Try This!","line_2_text":"I have been in search of a product for my dry itchy cracked skin. After only one week of applying this to my hands my arms my legs my feet and my lips - I still can't believe how good this product is."}},"step_eiWpDM":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Kim M.","filter_tag":"dry","line_1_text":"No Smell, Glided On Smoothly","line_2_text":"I love the texture and appreciate that there is no smell. It glided on smoothly and had absorbed into my skin by morning. Great product!"}},"step_BaBncY":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Mia D.","filter_tag":"dry","line_1_text":"This Is The Absolute Best","line_2_text":"The texture is extremely smooth and leaves your skin feeling hydrated. Highly Recommend"}},"step_8EHmgx":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Danielle B.","filter_tag":"anti-aging","line_1_text":"No One Can Guess My Age","line_2_text":"My fine lines have decreased by at least 75% and my discoloration sun spots have lightened. I refuse to use anything else on my face\/neck\/chest. Absolutely recommend."}},"step_cAYM9q":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Toni D.","filter_tag":"anti-aging","line_1_text":"Total Game Changer","line_2_text":"The texture is incredibly silky and it visibly plumps my skin, smoothing out fine lines and leaving a youthful radiance. My skin hasn't felt this firm or hydrated in years. HIGHLY RECOMMEND!"}},"step_YBxN6Q":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Sam A.","filter_tag":"anti-aging","line_1_text":"Absolutely Love This Product!","line_2_text":"I have been using for almost 4 weeks and have noticed an overall glow and improvement with fine lines\/blemishes on my face. This has also helped with my Psoriasis without the steroids that my prescriptions contain."}},"step_6Cj3c6":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Brooke B.","filter_tag":"acne","line_1_text":"My Acne Is Healing Up!","line_2_text":"I've only used it for 2 days and I'd have to say, my acne is healing up. It smells nice as well."}},"step_MqtNGj":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Juanita M.","filter_tag":"acne","line_1_text":"Doesn't Clog Your Pores","line_2_text":"It leaves your skin feeling so soft and it doesn’t clog your pores! It doesn't look like a greasy mess."}},"step_Aig3Ma":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Nicole P.","filter_tag":"acne","line_1_text":"It Turned My Skin Around","line_2_text":"My skin is not as dry or chapped. It hasn't cause any sort of irritation or breakouts. I'm very happy with the products and even used a little on my 4 month old as well for some drool rash."}}},"block_order":["step_GBW7Ew","step_3DAyfe","step_CbgTRp","step_VJrx89","step_eiWpDM","step_BaBncY","step_8EHmgx","step_cAYM9q","step_YBxN6Q","step_6Cj3c6","step_MqtNGj","step_Aig3Ma"],"name":"HT Review Slider","settings":{"show_trust_badge":true,"star_color":"#ff8a00","review_text_color":"#ffffff","reference_product":"{{ product }}","review_boost":0,"override_avg":"","review_text":"[avg]\/5 from 1000+ orders","main_title":"Made For Everyone","sub_title":"One pure ingredient. Countless skin transformations. A few of our favorites below"}},"ht_how_to_use_ttrezh":{"type":"ht-how-to-use","disabled":true,"name":"HT How To Use","settings":{}},"ht_howtouse_beforeafter_combined_Q9zcYB":{"type":"ht-howtouse_beforeafter_combined","name":"HT Transformation Hub","settings":{"subheading":"EXPERIENCE THE TRANSFORMATION","heading":"Before & After Hide Tallow","brand_name":"Hide Tallow","before_list":"{{ product.metafields.custom.pdp_before.value }}","after_list":"{{ product.metafields.custom.pdp_after.value }}","main_title":"","footer_image":"{{ product.metafields.custom.how_to_use_photo.value }}","heading_size_desktop":60,"heading_size_mobile":28,"pill_font_size":16,"padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"ht_pdp_other_products_3GHixe":{"type":"ht-pdp-other-products","blocks":{"product_PrmQhy":{"type":"product","settings":{"product":"the-everyday-jar","custom_desc":"The gold standard for full-body recovery. This whipped formula sinks deep to end chronic dryness and irritation, leaving a soft, velvet finish.","btn_text":"Explore"}},"product_PDP4xw":{"type":"product","settings":{"product":"on-the-go-tin","custom_desc":"Heavy-duty protection for your hardest-working skin. This firm balm creates a weather-proof barrier to seal and repair on the move","btn_text":"Explore"}},"product_XVyMyG":{"type":"product","settings":{"product":"the-pocket-stick","custom_desc":"Your daily defense against cracked lips. One swipe delivers deep hydration to restore elasticity and prevent chapping in any environment","btn_text":"Explore"}},"product_MgGhHd":{"type":"product","settings":{"product":"tallow-soap-bar","custom_desc":"A full-body reset that cleans without compromise. This tallow-rich bar lifts away grime while keeping your skin hydrated and smooth.","btn_text":"Explore"}},"product_zctTTy":{"type":"product","settings":{"product":"the-styler-jar","custom_desc":"A deep-root revival that styles without sacrifice. Tames stray strands and locks in moisture, keeping your hair hydrated, healthy, and perfectly held.","btn_text":"Explore"}},"product_VRdTaX":{"type":"product","settings":{"product":"shade","custom_desc":"A sun-drenched shield that protects without chemicals. This tallow-based barrier reflects harsh rays while nourishing your skin with deep, mineral-rich hydration.","btn_text":"Explore"}}},"block_order":["product_PrmQhy","product_PDP4xw","product_XVyMyG","product_MgGhHd","product_zctTTy","product_VRdTaX"],"name":"HT PDP Other Products","settings":{"heading":"Explore All Products"}},"ht_tallow_explained_ncC44A":{"type":"ht-tallow-explained","blocks":{"item_J464nM":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"What is Tallow?","content":"<p>Tallow is a nutrient-dense, purified form of grass-fed beef fat that has been used for centuries as a foundational skin remedy. Because it is bio-identical to the sebum produced by human skin, it is recognized and absorbed as a skin-native ingredient rather than a foreign wax or oil.<\/p>"}},"item_H4hfCi":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"Why Does Tallow Work?","content":"<p>Bio-identical to human sebum, tallow penetrates deep into the dermis to repair the skin barrier at a cellular level. It delivers essential fatty acids and vitamins exactly where your skin needs them most, mimicking your natural oils to hydrate without clogging pores.<\/p>"}},"item_kYU8rF":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"The Grass-Fed Difference","content":"<p>Our 100% grass-fed tallow provides 5x more CLA to soothe redness, essential vitamins A, D, E, and K for cellular repair, and powerful antioxidants for age-defying results. Unlike grain-fed alternatives, grass-fed tallow maintains a perfect balance of nutrients that your skin can actually utilize.<\/p>"}},"item_xPQrf6":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"Will Tallow cause acne?","content":"<p>Actually, no. Tallow is non-comedogenic, meaning it won’t clog your pores. Because its fatty acid profile matches your skin so closely, your body recognizes it and pulls it in rather than letting it sit on the surface like heavy waxes or petroleum-based oils.<\/p>"}},"item_FpFVQX":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"Is it safe for sensitive Skin","content":"<p>Yes. We use zero synthetic fragrances, parabens, or harsh chemicals. It’s just pure, grass-fed tallow and natural ingredients. It’s literally the most \"native\" thing you can put on your skin, making it ideal for those who react to everything else.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["item_J464nM","item_H4hfCi","item_kYU8rF","item_xPQrf6","item_FpFVQX"],"name":"HT Explained Section","settings":{"bg_color":"#0e3a27","text_color":"#ffffff","sub_heading":"BOOSTING YOUR SKIN HEALTH","main_heading":"Tallow Explained"}},"ht_brand_story_8a4iPq":{"type":"ht-brand-story","blocks":{"pillar_reChdX":{"type":"pillar","settings":{"icon_svg":"check","label":"Radical Purity","description":"Providing truly clean, tallow-based products that families can trust without second-guessing the label."}},"pillar_TPVNYn":{"type":"pillar","settings":{"icon_svg":"piggy","label":"Fair Pricing","description":"We are ending the trend of price gouging in the tallow industry to ensure healthy skin is affordable for everyone."}},"pillar_YyHVJV":{"type":"pillar","settings":{"icon_svg":"usa","label":"American Sourced","description":"Every jar is built on ingredients from local family farms, ensuring quality and transparency from the start."}},"pillar_wU9kWE":{"type":"pillar","settings":{"icon_svg":"heart","label":"Direct Impact","description":"We donate a portion of our proceeds directly to individuals and families impacted by cancer who are in need of help."}}},"block_order":["pillar_reChdX","pillar_TPVNYn","pillar_YyHVJV","pillar_wU9kWE"],"name":"HT Mission Pillars","settings":{"bg_color":"#ffffff","content_width":1100,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":25,"title_font":"Bricolage Grotesque","body_font":"Questrial","title_color":"#0e3a27","title_size":26,"intro_color":"#444444","intro_size":16,"mission_statement_color":"#0e3a27","mission_size":20,"pillar_title_color":"#0e3a27","icon_color":"#0e3a27","dot_active_color":"#0e3a27","border_color":"#e5e9e4","padding_icons":0,"icon_width":40,"icon_text_color":"#666666","icon_text_size":14,"title":"Our Commitment to You","intro_text":"We believe pure skincare should be accessible to every family. Our mission is to provide clean, honest products at fair prices, while using our growth to support those walking the path we once did.","mission_statement":"CLEAN. AFFORDABLE. HONEST."}},"ht_faq_yihXpW":{"type":"ht-faq","blocks":{"faq_item_YyGCmk":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"Where is Hide Tallow Based?","answer":"<p>We were proudly founded in 2024 and are currently based in <em><strong>Scottsdale, Arizona<\/strong><\/em>. <\/p>"}},"faq_item_DyQKk8":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"Where are Hide Tallow's Products manufactured?","answer":"<p>All of our products are proudly manufactured in the USA. We handle everything in small batches, from rendering and purifying to whipping and pouring, to ensure every jar meets our high standards for ancestral skin nutrition. <\/p>"}},"faq_item_bTtmLj":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"Where does Hide Tallow source their Tallow?","answer":"<p>We believe the quality of the tallow is only as good as the life of the animal. We meticulously source our suet from trusted farmers across the United States who prioritize soil health and animal welfare. <\/p><p>Currently, our 100% grass-fed and finished tallow is sourced from a <strong>small family farm in Delaware<\/strong>, ensuring we use only the highest quality suet for skin nourishment. <\/p>"}},"faq_item_RK8CTG":{"type":"faq_item","settings":{"question":"How long of a shelf life do Hide Tallow products have?","answer":"<p>Because our tallow is meticulously and contains zero water or synthetic fillers, it is naturally shelf-stable. Our products have a shelf life of <strong>12 months <\/strong>from the date of opening. <\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq_item_YyGCmk","faq_item_DyQKk8","faq_item_bTtmLj","faq_item_RK8CTG"],"name":"HT FAQ Premium","settings":{"main_title":"FAQs","main_subtext":"Everything you need to know about Hide Tallow.","max_width":900,"margin_top":20,"margin_bottom":80,"color_section_bg":"#ffffff","color_heading":"#0e3a27","color_subheading":"#4a4a4a","color_question_bg":"#f9faf8","color_question_text":"#0e3a27","color_answer_bg":"#ffffff","color_body_text":"#333333","color_